What is OmPad?

OmPad is a notepad to store notes, texts or even poems. It is focused in simplicity and speed for quick note taking and instant inspiration. You can choose different themes to the left and you have up to 5 note slots to save different topics. Go full screen and start typing!


About the app

OmPad is build with HTML5, CSS3 and jQuery. It is a great example on how modern websites can be so simple and tiny yet so functional. OmPad is a one-file app. Great for students and curious developers. You can grab the code and create your own version and styles. All the notes and settings are saved through HTML5 storage, this allows you to use OmPad also while being offline.


